 of this program, potential students may also contact Dr. Bertina Combes (Bertina.Combes@unt.edu).   AttachmentSize PHD-Mild-Moderate-Disabilities-Degree-Plan.docx25.33 KB Back to Masters and Doctoral Programs Department of Educational Psychology Contact Information College of Education Matthews Hall, Room 214 1300 West Highland Street Denton, TX 76203 Contact the College of Education Email Us For technical problems with this web site, contact COEWeb@unt.edu.     UNT System UNT System UNT Dallas Campus UNT Health Science Center Universities Center at Dallas Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy Statement | Web Accessibility Policy | State of Texas Online Go to Secure Login Page 